      <title></title>
      <url>/2020/08/01/%E5%8D%95%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="单应用程序部署"><a href="#单应用程序部署" class="headerlink" title="单应用程序部署"></a>单应用程序部署</h1><h2 id="docker部署"><a href="#docker部署" class="headerlink" title="docker部署"></a>docker部署</h2><ol>
<li><p>编写Dockerfile，新建一个Dockerfile，输入下面内容</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Docker image for springboot file run</span><br><span class="line"># VERSION 0.0.1</span><br><span class="line"># Author: liubingxu</span><br><span class="line">FROM java:8</span><br><span class="line">MAINTAINER eangulee &lt;liubingxu18@gmail.com&gt;</span><br><span class="line"># VOLUME 指定了临时文件目录为&#x2F;tmp。</span><br><span class="line"># 其效果是在主机 &#x2F;var&#x2F;lib&#x2F;docker 目录下创建了一个临时文件，并链接到容器的&#x2F;tmp</span><br><span class="line">VOLUME &#x2F;tmp</span><br><span class="line"># 将jar包添加到容器中并更名为app.jar</span><br><span class="line">ADD target&#x2F;demo-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar app.jar</span><br><span class="line"># 运行jar包</span><br><span class="line">RUN echo &quot;Asia&#x2F;Shanghai&quot; &gt; &#x2F;etc&#x2F;timezone</span><br><span class="line">RUN dpkg-reconfigure -f noninteractive tzdata</span><br><span class="line">RUN bash -c &#39;touch &#x2F;app.jar&#39;</span><br><span class="line">ENTRYPOINT [&quot;java&quot;,&quot;-Djava.security.egd&#x3D;file:&#x2F;dev&#x2F;.&#x2F;urandom&quot;,&quot;-jar&quot;,&quot;&#x2F;app.jar&quot;]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>编写Linux启动脚本，输入下面内容</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mvn clean package -Dmaven.test.skip&#x3D;true</span><br><span class="line">containerName&#x3D;&quot;app-name&quot;</span><br><span class="line">imageName&#x3D;&quot;app-name-container&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">docker stop $&#123;containerName&#125;</span><br><span class="line">docker rm $&#123;containerName&#125;</span><br><span class="line">docker rmi $&#123;imageName&#125;:latest</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">docker build -t $&#123;imageName&#125; .</span><br><span class="line">docker run -d --privileged --name $&#123;containerName&#125; -v &#x2F;etc&#x2F;localtime:&#x2F;etc&#x2F;localtime -v &#x2F;home&#x2F;logs&#x2F;$&#123;containerName&#125;:&#x2F;tmp -p 80:80 $&#123;imageName&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">docker logs -f $&#123;containerName&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>将Windows格式文本转换成Linux格式</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dos2unix + filename</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>编写Windows启动脚本，输入下面内容</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">call mvn clean package -Dmaven.test.skip&#x3D;true</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">docker stop app-name</span><br><span class="line">docker rm app-name</span><br><span class="line">docker rmi app-name-container:latest</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">docker build -t app-name-container .</span><br><span class="line">docker run --name app-name -p 80:80 app-name-container</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="服务形式部署"><a href="#服务形式部署" class="headerlink" title="服务形式部署"></a>服务形式部署</h2><ol>
<li><p>pom添加服务化支持</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;plugin&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;&#x2F;groupId&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-maven-plugin&lt;&#x2F;artifactId&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;configuration&gt;</span><br><span class="line">       &lt;executable&gt;true&lt;&#x2F;executable&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;&#x2F;configuration&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;plugin&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>编写start.sh</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mvn clean package -Dmaven.test.skip&#x3D;true</span><br><span class="line">service myapp stop</span><br><span class="line">workDir&#x3D;$(pwd)</span><br><span class="line">echo $&#123;workDir&#125;</span><br><span class="line">rm -rf &#x2F;etc&#x2F;init.d&#x2F;myapp</span><br><span class="line">chmod +x $&#123;workDir&#125;&#x2F;target&#x2F;demo-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar</span><br><span class="line">sudo ln -s $&#123;workDir&#125;&#x2F;target&#x2F;demo-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar &#x2F;etc&#x2F;init.d&#x2F;myapp</span><br><span class="line">service myapp start</span><br><span class="line">tail -f &#x2F;var&#x2F;log&#x2F;myapp.log</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ol>
]]></content>
      
        
    </entry>
    
